{{Quote|Want to negotiate a landing fee?''"<br />''"Want to negotiate an ion cannon?''"<br />"''Oh...apologies, Master Fett, sir...|Atzerri Air Traffic Control and [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]]|<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Bloodlines">''[[Legacy of the Force: Bloodlines]]''</ref>}}
The '''Atzerri Air Traffic Control''' was established at some point before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], and regulated comings and goings from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Atzerri/Legends|Atzerri]].

The [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Elmyo]] and a [[Unidentified Gotal traffic controller|Gotal male]] were members of the traffic control. When the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] was turning his [[Bounty/Legends|bounty]], the Atzerri [[Glitterstim/Legends|glitterstim]] dealer [[H'buk]], over to the [[Traders' Coalition]], the traffic controller tried to negotiate the landing fee with Fett.

